catastrophic library), you grant Oliver Uvman the right to distribute
your contribution under the Apache 2.0 license or any GPLv2 compatible
license as recognized by the Free Software Foundation.

I try to optimize the API to this library for clients' convenience,
so please ask before you start coding on any contributions. There's
a large risk that I might want to give you some feedback on the API
design.

Please also include tests for any contribution you make, see the tests
directory.
